<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>✨ ZVW3 | Test Site</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, -apple-system, 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0c29, #302b63, #24243e);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .glass-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border-radius: 2rem;
            padding: 3rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 45px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3), 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .glass-card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.01);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, #fff, #a78bfa);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.3);
            padding: 0.3rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 40px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #c4b5fd;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.5);
        }

        .status {
            background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.2);
            border-left: 4px solid #22c55e;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
        }

        .status-dot {
            width: 12px;
            height: 12px;
            background: #22c55e;
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: pulse 1.5s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
            50% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(1.2); }
        }

        .status-text {
            color: #bbf7d0;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        p {
            color: #e2e8f0;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }

        .button-group {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 40px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #8b5cf6, #6d28d9);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.5);
        }

        .btn-outline {
            background: transparent;
            border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.6);
            color: #c4b5fd;
        }

        .btn-outline:hover {
            background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
            border-color: #8b5cf6;
        }

        .info-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
        }

        .info-item {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .info-label {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            color: #9ca3af;
        }

        .info-value {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #a78bfa;
            margin-top: 0.25rem;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        @media (max-width: 500px) {
            .glass-card { padding: 1.5rem; }
            h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
            .info-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="glass-card">
        <div class="badge">✨ GitHub Pages • Live</div>
        <h1>Test site<br>is working 🚀</h1>
        
        <div class="status">
            <div class="status-dot"></div>
            <span class="status-text">• Deployment successful •</span>
        </div>

        <p>
            If you're seeing this fancy UI, your GitHub Pages setup is <strong>working perfectly</strong>.
            The file is now named <code style="background:rgba(0,0,0,0.3);padding:2px 6px;border-radius:6px;">index.html</code> 
            and the site is live at:
        </p>

        <div class="info-grid">
            <div class="info-item">
                <div class="info-label">Your Repo</div>
                <div class="info-value">zvw3/reto</div>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <div class="info-label">Live URL</div>
                <div class="info-value">zvw3.github.io/reto</div>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <div class="info-label">Status</div>
                <div class="info-value">✅ Active</div>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <div class="info-label">Server</div>
                <div class="info-value">GitHub Pages</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="button-group">
            <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="alert('✨ GitHub Pages is working! Your site is live.')">Click to Test</button>
            <a href="https://github.com/zvw3/reto" class="btn btn-outline" target="_blank">View on GitHub →</a>
        </div>

        <footer>
            deployed via GitHub Pages • 2026
        </footer>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Console confirmation
        console.log("🎉 Fancy UI loaded — GitHub Pages is working!");
    </script>
</body>
</html>
